chunks.content: Another radio station, WVFI, began as a partner of WSND-FM. More recently, however, WVFI has been airing independently and is streamed on the Internet.

metadata.relevance_reason: This part directly mentions that WVFI is an internet radio station that is streamed on the Internet.
metadata.answer_contribution: Identifies WVFI as the internet radio station of Notre Dame that serves as an internet stream.

required_info: name of the internet radio station
